## v5.19 - Verify that all input data is validated, not only HTML form fields but all sources of input such as REST calls, query parameters, HTTP headers, cookies, batch files, RSS feeds, etc; using positive validation (whitelisting), then lesser forms of validation such as greylisting (eliminating known bad strings), or rejecting bad inputs (blacklisting).

