### Applicability (Level 2)

This objective applies to all apps.

### Guidelines for developers

Treat all user input as malicious: validate for length and content, escape any special characters, and parameterize any queries.  Create architecture that minimizes need for direct user input.  Any input coming from third-party sources must only be permitted from whitelisted sources.
